# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Career Navigator - Client Environment Variables (Template)
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Usage:
# 1) Copy this file to `.env` (or `.env.local`)
# 2) Fill in required values
# 3) NEVER commit your real `.env` (secrets) to git
#
# Notes (Vite):
# - Only variables prefixed with `VITE_` are exposed to the browser.
# - Avoid putting secrets here. Anything in the client env is public.
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------

# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# API
# -----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Base URL for the backend server.
# Examples:
# - Local:   http://localhost:5000
# - Hosted:  https://api.your-domain.com
VITE_API_URL=http://localhost:5000